---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute Events - Find Local Chess">
  <div>
    <section>
      <h1>Contribute Events</h1>
      
      <p>
        Help us keep Find Local Chess up to date! This website is community-driven, 
        and we welcome contributions from anyone who knows about local chess events.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to Add an Event</h2>
      
      <div>
        <div>
          <div>1</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Fork the Repository</h3>
            <p>
              Visit our <a href="https://github.com/your-username/chess-website" target="_blank">GitHub repository</a> 
              and click the "Fork" button to create your own copy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div>2</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Create Your Event File</h3>
            <p>
              Navigate to <code>src/content/events/</code> and create a new markdown file 
              with a descriptive filename (e.g., <code>spring-tournament-2025.md</code>).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div>3</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Use the Template</h3>
            <p>Copy the template below and fill in your event details.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div>4</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Submit a Pull Request</h3>
            <p>
              Commit your changes and create a pull request. We'll review it and 
              merge it if everything looks good!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Event Template</h2>
      
      <p>Copy this template to create a new event file:</p>
      
      <div>
        <pre><code>---
title: "Your Event Title"
date: 2025-02-15
time: "7:00 PM"
location: "Venue Name"
address: "123 Street Name, City, State 12345"
description: "Brief description of your event"
link: "https://example.com/more-info"
organizer: "Organization or Person Name"
contact: "email@example.com"
entryFee: "$10"
timeControl: "90+30 (90 minutes + 30 second increment)"
rounds: 5
tags: ["tournament", "classical", "weekend"]
---

Add your detailed event description here using Markdown formatting.

## What to Expect

- Detail about the event
- Registration information
- Prize structure
- Any special rules

## How to Register

Include registration details, deadlines, and any requirements.

For questions, contact [organizer name] at [contact info].</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Field Guidelines</h2>
      
      <div>
        <div>
          <h3>Required Fields</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>title:</strong> Clear, descriptive event name</li>
            <li><strong>date:</strong> Event date in YYYY-MM-DD format</li>
            <li><strong>time:</strong> Start time (include timezone if needed)</li>
            <li><strong>location:</strong> Venue name</li>
            <li><strong>description:</strong> Brief 1-2 sentence summary</li>
            <li><strong>organizer:</strong> Person or organization running the event</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>Optional Fields</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>address:</strong> Full address for the venue</li>
            <li><strong>link:</strong> Website URL for more information</li>
            <li><strong>contact:</strong> Email address for questions</li>
            <li><strong>entryFee:</strong> Cost to participate</li>
            <li><strong>timeControl:</strong> Chess time control format</li>
            <li><strong>rounds:</strong> Number of tournament rounds</li>
            <li><strong>tags:</strong> Categories like "tournament", "casual", "blitz"</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Content Guidelines</h2>
      
      <div>
        <h3>✅ Please Include:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Accurate date, time, and location information</li>
          <li>Clear description of the event format</li>
          <li>Registration requirements and deadlines</li>
          <li>Contact information for questions</li>
          <li>Any special rules or requirements</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>❌ Please Avoid:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Promotional language or excessive marketing</li>
          <li>Events that have already passed</li>
          <li>Duplicate entries for the same event</li>
          <li>Personal contact information in public descriptions</li>
          <li>Misleading or inaccurate information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Need Help?</h2>
      
      <p>
        If you're not comfortable with GitHub or need assistance, you can:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/your-username/chess-website/issues" target="_blank">
            Create an issue
          </a> with your event details and we'll add it for you
        </li>
        <li>Email us at [maintainer-email] with your event information</li>
        <li>Ask for help in our community discussions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>